@title Contribution Pathways: Governance Follows Contribution
@keywords co-producers, contribution, collective-choice, governance-standing, contribution-log, steering-group, mentoring, ORCA, Community-of-Practice, activation, cognitive-participation, NPT, Sen, Ostrom, architecture-tier, high-coordination, capability-return
